{"tid":1649020,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你覺得十八區太散, 下次可以考慮下五區","createTime":"2019-10-12T13:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T13:12:49.000Z","uid":11454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"efd86158692ed21edf20b51a472d2e4a013ee018","tid":1649020,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:02:56.000Z","msg":"港島: 銅鑼灣<br />\n九龍東: 觀塘/黃大仙<br />\n九龍西: 深水埗<br />\n新界西: 荃灣/元朗<br />\n新界東; 沙田 <br />\n<br />\n8月5搞得掂, 只要團結, 和勇不分<br />\n香港人一定可以搞得掂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0deeb3dede7a300cc0f3429409f09a900c1f9c6","tid":1649020,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"bb43ae7596ee9bbb23da50916a7e887c2c1aa910","tid":1649020,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa309023b88afa30e2cf842a19d08682c5be312","tid":1649020,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"a14a00a2a946841c42eaae47fda12f06e4741a26","tid":1649020,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"[行動POST] 想要靚畫面？銀髮族48小時靜坐咪就係機會囉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648992</a><br />\n<br />\n警總靜坐現場，有老人有中年人有外國人有後生仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多中年帶哂席同櫈黎，準備過夜。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">想有新行動？想要靚畫面？咁你就快啲過黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日攰唔出都唔緊要，準備聽日接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我煲大佢，唔好當銀髮手足係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAwXWg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAwXWg8.jpg&h=aab0f8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0700bfd2a94628aa2cb3417470a813c2b15d032","tid":1649020,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點係太多行動, 分散哂人數+撞哂時間<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人最鍾意係跟風</span><br />\n太多活動=人數自然少=俾狗咬機會變大=少人參與<br />\n<br />\n集番5區, 每區最少10萬唔成問題<br />\n人愈多, 和勇愈安全<br />\n<br />\n單線同十八地區開花<br />\n我相信大家都係搵緊個平衡點<br />\n係需要時間, 唔好因為一個星期就失去信心而灰心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">依場仗一定要嬴, 一定要一齊嬴</span></span>"},{"pid":"13f03f2fa0e0dd7660dbcf2754328d2777e4e23e","tid":1649020,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkCPL7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkCPL7d.jpg&h=0de258de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZxHmFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZxHmFA.jpg&h=034607b8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}